properties.name: Burr Oak
properties.characteristics: Recongized by it's bass fiddle shaped leaves and large fringe capped acorns, the bur oak can live for hundreds of years.

properties.name: Possumhaw Viburnum
properties.characteristics: Varies from red to purple. No real pest concerns and it is adaptable to sun or shade. Medicines made from the plant have been utilized for centuries.
